@using OpenCaptive.Application.Email.Models
@model VerifyEmailTemplateModel
@{
    var hours = (int)Math.Round(Model.TokenLifetime.TotalHours);
}
Verify your email

Hi @Model.RecipientFirstName,

Thanks for creating an OpenCaptive account. Confirm this is your email address to activate your account by opening the link below:

@Raw(Model.VerificationUrl)

This link expires in @hours hours and can only be used once. If it expires, you can request a new verification email from the sign-in page.

If you didn't create an OpenCaptive account, you can safely ignore this email — no account will be activated.

--
You received this email because an OpenCaptive account was created with this email address.
Need help? @Raw(ViewBag.SupportUrl)
@Raw(ViewBag.WebsiteUrl)

(c) @DateTime.UtcNow.Year @ViewBag.BrandName. All rights reserved.
